Procedure.description:
Procedure Purpose: FCI Activation WAIT to OBSERVATION
Procedure Version: 2 Responsibility: Claudia Tranquilli Last Modified Date: 13.12.2022 Change History:
Version 2: (CT - 13.12.2022) - Updated arguments/variables for PAF selection of MS and REPSEQ.
Version 1: (CT - 25.07.2022) - Master procedure created to handle scan setup from WAIT to OBSERVATION mode.
Procedure Objectives:
- This procedure performs scan scenario setup and WP start. Depending on the selected END_MODE, after execution FCI will be in WAIT with Scan Scenario (SL, SSL, REPSEQ) loaded and selected, or in OBSERVATION.
Procedure Overview:
This procedure performs the following activities: - Identify season and select correct PAFs w.r.t. MS and scan pattern; - Setup the Scan Scenario; - Start the Work Plan.
Procedure Pre-conditions: S/C in FPM/NOM
Procedure Constraints: None
Spacecraft Configuration: FPM/NOM
Ground Segment Configuration: None
Remarks: PAFs for the update of MS, REPSEQ and INSTCONF are required.
